reviews.review_text:
An excellent Audience. I won't review the show as that's been done ad nausea.  However,  This is an excellent audience recording and transfer.  Very clean, wonderful sense of space.  For those that have the playback system... this is worth a listen as an excellent alternative to the other offerings here.

Thanks for the Tunes!
